288
00:12:52,180 --> 00:12:53,820
you know Anlan well.

289
00:12:54,820 --> 00:12:56,740
Honestly, I haven't known Anlan long,

290
00:12:57,220 --> 00:12:58,860
but when I'm with him,

291
00:12:58,860 --> 00:13:00,580
I just feel completely at ease.

292
00:13:00,900 --> 00:13:02,540
I don't have to guess
what he's thinking.

293
00:13:03,020 --> 00:13:04,060
He always manages

294
00:13:04,060 --> 00:13:05,440
to handle everything so thoroughly.

295
00:13:06,700 --> 00:13:07,820
Anlan's dad

296
00:13:07,820 --> 00:13:10,780
has been strict with him
since he was a kid.

297
00:13:10,780 --> 00:13:13,620
He always taught him to think carefully

298
00:13:14,460 --> 00:13:16,780
and to hold himself to higher standards.

299
00:13:17,180 --> 00:13:18,300
So,

300
00:13:18,300 --> 00:13:21,420
Anlan worked harder
than anyone could imagine.

301
00:13:21,420 --> 00:13:22,900
Only then could he become

302
00:13:22,900 --> 00:13:25,020
the favorite and the most valued

303
00:13:25,020 --> 00:13:26,380
of his father and even the elders

304
00:13:26,380 --> 00:13:28,900
of the entire family.

305
00:13:29,940 --> 00:13:30,780
Yao Yuan,

306
00:13:32,140 --> 00:13:34,620
being with Anlan
must be stressful for you.

307
00:13:36,980 --> 00:13:38,300
But I want to tell you:

308
00:13:38,740 --> 00:13:40,300
If you want to marry him,

309
00:13:40,300 --> 00:13:43,140
the pressure you'll face
will be even greater.

310
00:13:44,260 --> 00:13:45,400
Have you thought about that?

311
00:13:45,740 --> 00:13:47,660
If you keep it going with Anlan,

312
00:13:48,420 --> 00:13:49,660
can you handle it?

313
00:13:55,180 --> 00:13:56,780
(Lord of All)

314
00:13:59,220 --> 00:14:00,620
The driver should be here for me.

315
00:14:00,620 --> 00:14:01,580
I'll leave then.

316
00:14:02,160 --> 00:14:03,020
Goodbye, Mrs. Jiang.

317
00:14:03,020 --> 00:14:03,860
Goodbye.

318
00:14:13,700 --> 00:14:14,740
Hey, Anlan.

319
00:14:21,180 --> 00:14:22,780
Where did you go with my mom today?

320
00:14:23,300 --> 00:14:24,140
We went for coffee

321
00:14:24,540 --> 00:14:25,960
and picked out a gift for your dad.

322
00:14:26,740 --> 00:14:28,700
Your mom even gave me a silk scarf.

323
00:14:29,860 --> 00:14:30,740
I didn't expect

324
00:14:30,740 --> 00:14:32,140
you'd hit it off so fast.

325
00:14:35,220 --> 00:14:36,540
Jianing told me

326
00:14:36,540 --> 00:14:37,700
you had a fight with your dad.

327
00:14:38,420 --> 00:14:40,140
Should I go apologize?

328
00:14:40,940 --> 00:14:42,020
Apologize for what?

329
00:14:42,020 --> 00:14:42,980
It's not your fault.

330
00:14:45,380 --> 00:14:46,740
If you weren't taking care of me,

331
00:14:46,900 --> 00:14:48,940
you wouldn't have missed
your dad's birthday party,

332
00:14:49,140 --> 00:14:50,540
and you wouldn't have argued.

333
00:14:51,940 --> 00:14:53,700
I do have some conflicts with my dad,

334
00:14:54,060 --> 00:14:55,300
but it's not because of you.

335
00:14:56,620 --> 00:14:57,820
Since I was a kid,

336
00:14:58,260 --> 00:14:59,780
I've always worked hard to complete

337
00:14:59,780 --> 00:15:01,260
all the tasks he gave me.

338
00:15:02,340 --> 00:15:03,820
Our conversations always revolved

339
00:15:03,820 --> 00:15:05,660
around how to set goals

340
00:15:05,660 --> 00:15:06,980
and how to reach them.

341
00:15:07,940 --> 00:15:08,860
After growing up,

342
00:15:09,380 --> 00:15:10,260
except for work,

343
00:15:10,900 --> 00:15:11,740
I don't know how

344
00:15:11,740 --> 00:15:13,060
to get closer to him.

345
00:15:15,380 --> 00:15:17,020
But your dad still loves you;

346
00:15:17,420 --> 00:15:19,100
otherwise, he wouldn't care

347
00:15:19,100 --> 00:15:20,220
whether you were there.

348
00:15:21,400 --> 00:15:22,580
I just wanted to simply send

349
00:15:22,580 --> 00:15:24,300
a birthday wish,

350
00:15:24,820 --> 00:15:26,200
not to play the role of a good son

351
00:15:26,200 --> 00:15:27,420
in front of everyone.

352
00:15:30,060 --> 00:15:32,060
But you are your dad's good son.

353
00:15:33,420 --> 00:15:34,820
I honestly envy you

354
00:15:34,820 --> 00:15:36,900
for having a dad
who nurtures you so well.

355
00:15:37,920 --> 00:15:39,100
He plans everything for you,

356
00:15:39,100 --> 00:15:40,420
sending you to do so many things.

357
00:15:40,420 --> 00:15:41,680
He just wants the best for you.

358
00:15:42,020 --> 00:15:43,500
If you didn't have such a great dad,

359
00:15:43,500 --> 00:15:45,300
I wouldn't have such a good boyfriend.

360
00:15:46,740 --> 00:15:48,660
I wish I could be as comfortable

361
00:15:49,500 --> 00:15:51,260
with my family as with you.

362
00:15:51,820 --> 00:15:53,620
If you spent more time and effort

363
00:15:53,620 --> 00:15:55,080
on your mom and dad,

364
00:15:55,100 --> 00:15:56,180
you'd feel just as at ease.

365
00:15:57,860 --> 00:15:58,700
Alright then.

366
00:16:28,220 --> 00:16:30,100
(Can I really go on with Anlan?)

367
00:16:40,260 --> 00:16:41,100
(No.)

368
00:16:41,740 --> 00:16:43,260
(I can't become a burden to Anlan.)

369
00:16:49,580 --> 00:16:53,060
(Mrs. Jiang)

370
00:17:02,860 --> 00:17:04,340
Hi, Mrs. Jiang. This is Yao Yuan.

371
00:17:04,940 --> 00:17:05,820
This is Yao Yuan.

372
00:17:06,580 --> 00:17:08,260
I want to ask you for a favor.

373
00:17:09,060 --> 00:17:09,900
Xinran.

374
00:17:10,340 --> 00:17:11,300
Please forgive me.

375
00:17:12,350 --> 00:17:13,740
What is there to forgive?

376
00:17:14,020 --> 00:17:15,460
She made the move.

377
00:17:15,940 --> 00:17:17,020
I'm talking about Yuting.

378
00:17:17,020 --> 00:17:17,980
She took the initiative.

379
00:17:18,260 --> 00:17:19,700
But I've made it clear to her.

380
00:17:21,060 --> 00:17:21,960
Really.

381
00:17:21,960 --> 00:17:23,620
I mean, I firmly

382
00:17:23,620 --> 00:17:24,990
and clearly rejected her.

383
00:17:25,220 --> 00:17:27,580
I'll prevent this from happening again.

384
00:17:28,180 --> 00:17:29,220
What's it to me?

385
00:17:35,580 --> 00:17:37,980
All along, I haven't been honest enough.

386
00:17:39,540 --> 00:17:40,380
I've been avoiding

387
00:17:40,380 --> 00:17:42,260
the shadow left by my parents' divorce.

388
00:17:43,300 --> 00:17:44,980
I tried to find faults in others

389
00:17:45,460 --> 00:17:46,980
to cover up my own insecurity.

390
00:17:51,060 --> 00:17:52,660
I've finally figured out my own issues.

391
00:17:53,480 --> 00:17:54,480
Only then did I realize

392
00:17:55,800 --> 00:17:57,780
you're just afraid of getting hurt
by love again.

393
00:17:58,100 --> 00:17:59,540
That's why you've been avoiding me.

394
00:18:01,580 --> 00:18:02,720
I don't blame you for that.

395
00:18:02,980 --> 00:18:04,840
I know you're just trying
to protect yourself.

396
00:18:05,540 --> 00:18:06,500
But in truth,

397
00:18:07,420 --> 00:18:08,900
you care about me deep down.

398
00:18:11,580 --> 00:18:12,460
So,

399
00:18:14,620 --> 00:18:16,380
are you willing to be with me?

400
00:18:21,950 --> 00:18:22,820
If you really

401
00:18:22,820 --> 00:18:24,900
have no feelings for me, then I...

402
00:18:35,500 --> 00:18:36,540
What about Zhou?

403
00:18:36,700 --> 00:18:37,740
Aren't you two...

404
00:18:38,980 --> 00:18:40,020
You should ask Xiaoya.

405
00:18:40,340 --> 00:18:41,480
She'd be happy to tell you.

406
00:18:43,380 --> 00:18:44,660
Li Ao...

407
00:18:47,220 --> 00:18:51,620
♪Because you've completely won me over♪

408
00:18:51,620 --> 00:18:53,820
♪A little stubbornness, a few flaws♪

409
00:18:53,820 --> 00:18:56,060
♪You can always heal me♪

410
00:18:56,060 --> 00:18:59,440
♪You're the one sent by destiny♪

411
00:18:59,690 --> 00:19:03,080
♪It's you I love♪

412
00:19:12,940 --> 00:19:14,060
You must be Yao Yuan, right?

413
00:19:18,740 --> 00:19:19,860
Did you call me here today

414
00:19:21,300 --> 00:19:22,980
just to invite me for a coffee?

415
00:19:32,420 --> 00:19:33,260
Mr. Jiang,

416
00:19:35,100 --> 00:19:36,100
actually,

417
00:19:36,100 --> 00:19:37,700
I wanted to apologize to you.

418
00:19:38,900 --> 00:19:40,260
On your birthday,

419
00:19:40,740 --> 00:19:41,820
Anlan wasn't there.

420
00:19:41,820 --> 00:19:42,820
It's not her fault.

421
00:19:42,820 --> 00:19:43,600
I was sick.

422
00:19:43,600 --> 00:19:44,780
He wanted to take care of me,

423
00:19:44,780 --> 00:19:45,620
so...

424
00:19:50,940 --> 00:19:53,100
This is the birthday gift
I prepared for you.

425
00:19:53,900 --> 00:19:54,740
I hope you like it.

426
00:20:02,340 --> 00:20:03,180
Actually,

427
00:20:04,260 --> 00:20:05,700
Anlan cares about you a lot.

428
00:20:06,420 --> 00:20:07,260
Maybe

429
00:20:07,260 --> 00:20:08,660
he just doesn't know how to express

430
00:20:08,660 --> 00:20:09,460
what's on his mind.

431
00:20:11,500 --> 00:20:12,340
Got it.

432
00:20:15,020 --> 00:20:15,860
You came today

433
00:20:16,860 --> 00:20:18,900
to plead with me on Anlan's behalf.

434
00:20:22,300 --> 00:20:23,740
Anlan is my son.

435
00:20:25,380 --> 00:20:26,660
I know him better than you do.

436
00:20:27,700 --> 00:20:28,540
Honestly speaking,

437
00:20:29,740 --> 00:20:31,340
I'm against you two being together.

438
00:20:37,100 --> 00:20:38,460
I admire your courage,

439
00:20:40,980 --> 00:20:42,700
but it doesn't change anything.

440
00:20:44,340 --> 00:20:45,900
If you have nothing else to say,

441
00:20:47,060 --> 00:20:48,460
I have to go back to my office.

442
00:20:53,660 --> 00:20:54,540
Mr. Jiang,

443
00:20:56,900 --> 00:20:58,220
I won't give up on Anlan.

444
00:21:00,940 --> 00:21:02,100
I'm surely the one

445
00:21:02,100 --> 00:21:03,900
he can rely on and trust.

446
00:21:05,340 --> 00:21:07,260
You really sound like Anlan.

447
00:21:16,940 --> 00:21:18,900
Do you really think you're a good match?

448
00:21:26,420 --> 00:21:28,700
No one is born having it all.

449
00:21:30,380 --> 00:21:31,740
Anlan earned his success

450
00:21:31,740 --> 00:21:33,220
through his own hard work.

451
00:21:34,660 --> 00:21:35,800
I believe I can do the same.

452
00:21:40,060 --> 00:21:41,980
If this were a job interview,

453
00:21:43,500 --> 00:21:45,420
I might consider giving you a chance.

454
00:21:49,420 --> 00:21:50,580
But since this is about Anlan,

455
00:21:52,740 --> 00:21:54,380
your family background alone

456
00:21:55,060 --> 00:21:55,940
disqualifies you.

457
00:21:58,300 --> 00:21:59,300
Thanks for the coffee.

458
00:22:00,620 --> 00:22:01,700
I've paid for it.

459
00:22:12,780 --> 00:22:14,220
I'm still waiting for the chairman.

460
00:22:15,100 --> 00:22:15,940
Right.

461
00:22:16,180 --> 00:22:17,740
I'll tell him once he gets in the car.

462
00:22:19,940 --> 00:22:21,040
Looks like he's coming out.

463
00:22:21,380 --> 00:22:22,260
Okay, that's it.

464
00:22:24,260 --> 00:22:25,100
Mr. Jiang.

465
00:22:28,460 --> 00:22:29,300
Your gift.

466
00:22:29,700 --> 00:22:30,540
You didn't take it.

467
00:22:37,740 --> 00:22:38,580
I know

468
00:22:38,980 --> 00:22:40,380
you can't accept me yet,

469
00:22:41,540 --> 00:22:42,460
but I believe

470
00:22:43,220 --> 00:22:44,780
you will accept me one day.

471
00:22:48,060 --> 00:22:49,300
I won't keep the gift.

472
00:22:50,020 --> 00:22:51,340
I hope you'll reconsider

473
00:22:51,340 --> 00:22:52,860
your relationship with Anlan.

474
00:22:53,500 --> 00:22:54,380
Goodbye.

475
00:23:04,420 --> 00:23:05,420
(That girl)

476
00:23:05,420 --> 00:23:06,260
(looks so familiar.)

477
00:23:08,940 --> 00:23:10,860
(But I just can't remember)

478
00:23:10,860 --> 00:23:11,940
(who she is.)

479
00:23:17,980 --> 00:23:19,940
Let's conduct a review

480
00:23:19,940 --> 00:23:20,780
of the last M&A case.

481
00:23:21,180 --> 00:23:22,720
We all agree that Ancheng's acquisition

482
00:23:22,780 --> 00:23:24,860
of four companies in three months

483
00:23:25,020 --> 00:23:28,220
does meet the set KPI targets
in terms of numbers.

484
00:23:33,900 --> 00:23:34,820
I have a question.

485
00:23:35,660 --> 00:23:36,940
According to the finance report,

486
00:23:37,180 --> 00:23:38,980
last quarter's budget
was more than enough.

487
00:23:39,220 --> 00:23:40,380
What I don't get is

488
00:23:41,140 --> 00:23:42,700
why the group, with enough strength,

489
00:23:42,700 --> 00:23:44,140
could've acquired over six companies

490
00:23:44,190 --> 00:23:45,380
within three months,

491
00:23:46,540 --> 00:23:48,940
but you stopped after only four.

492
00:23:49,780 --> 00:23:50,740
You're right.

493
00:23:51,460 --> 00:23:54,180
We could've exceeded our KPI targets.

494
00:23:55,020 --> 00:23:57,100
I did consider two other companies

495
00:23:57,100 --> 00:23:58,580
as potential M&A targets.

496
00:23:59,460 --> 00:24:01,620
Why did you let

497
00:24:01,900 --> 00:24:03,540
the opportunity slip away?

498
00:24:04,100 --> 00:24:06,020
After a thorough evaluation,

499
00:24:06,020 --> 00:24:08,340
I found
their current systems to be weak.

500
00:24:08,820 --> 00:24:09,820
If we rushed

501
00:24:09,820 --> 00:24:10,740
the acquisition,

502
00:24:11,020 --> 00:24:13,140
the restructuring costs later on

503
00:24:13,140 --> 00:24:14,500
would far exceed our budget.

504
00:24:14,780 --> 00:24:16,620
That's why I paused the acquisition.

505
00:24:19,740 --> 00:24:20,860
Ancheng's foresight

506
00:24:21,500 --> 00:24:22,340
was indeed thorough.

507
00:24:23,380 --> 00:24:25,500
His decision actually helped us

508
00:24:25,500 --> 00:24:27,860
avoid financial risks in the merger.

509
00:24:28,540 --> 00:24:30,940
But we've been aiming
to expand market share.

510
00:24:31,380 --> 00:24:33,580
Their market share
and distribution channels

511
00:24:33,580 --> 00:24:34,900
are exactly what we need.

512
00:24:35,260 --> 00:24:37,300
Calling off the merger now
would be like giving up.

513
00:24:38,020 --> 00:24:38,940
That'd be a shame.

514
00:24:39,300 --> 00:24:40,500
We didn't give up.

515
00:24:40,960 --> 00:24:42,420
I've reached an agreement with them.

516
00:24:42,420 --> 00:24:44,700
We'll start by cooperating
through a strategic alliance.

517
00:24:44,980 --> 00:24:47,460
For these two companies
in urgent need of capital,

518
00:24:48,180 --> 00:24:49,680
our capital investment,

519
00:24:49,680 --> 00:24:51,020
collaborations on new technology,

520
00:24:51,020 --> 00:24:52,660
and new product development

521
00:24:52,980 --> 00:24:54,220
will be exchanged

522
00:24:54,220 --> 00:24:55,540
for their distribution channels,

523
00:24:55,540 --> 00:24:57,580
giving us access
to a larger potential client base.

524
00:24:58,860 --> 00:25:00,900
Exactly. The relevant contracts

525
00:25:01,100 --> 00:25:02,800
are being handled
by the legal department.

526
00:25:03,580 --> 00:25:05,540
The strategic alliance
will be launched soon.

527
00:25:09,500 --> 00:25:10,740
Like father,

528
00:25:10,740 --> 00:25:12,220
like son.

529
00:25:16,220 --> 00:25:17,500
Let's wrap up today's meeting.

530
00:25:18,500 --> 00:25:19,340
Thanks for your time.

531
00:25:57,220 --> 00:25:58,500
You're celebrating too soon.

532
00:26:02,660 --> 00:26:04,820
Some people might only offer
surface-level support.

533
00:26:08,460 --> 00:26:09,700
You did well this time.

534
00:26:11,740 --> 00:26:13,180
But next time, don't rush

535
00:26:13,180 --> 00:26:14,580
to lay all your cards on the table.

536
00:26:16,180 --> 00:26:17,820
First, assess the situation.

537
00:26:18,420 --> 00:26:19,700
Then wait for the right moment.

538
00:26:21,580 --> 00:26:22,420
I understand.

539
00:26:45,460 --> 00:26:46,300
Hey, Mr. Jiang.

540
00:26:46,940 --> 00:26:47,860
Why are you alone here?

541
00:26:47,860 --> 00:26:48,740
Well.

542
00:26:49,060 --> 00:26:50,180
You didn't bring a date?

543
00:26:52,100 --> 00:26:53,360
Something must be on your mind.

544
00:26:55,540 --> 00:26:56,380
Ancheng,

545
00:26:57,020 --> 00:26:58,720
when you become
Jiulong's general manager,

546
00:26:59,140 --> 00:27:00,220
don't forget about us.

547
00:27:02,180 --> 00:27:03,200
Between you two brothers,

548
00:27:03,240 --> 00:27:04,620
one takes over the family business;

549
00:27:04,620 --> 00:27:05,980
the other starts his own venture.

550
00:27:05,980 --> 00:27:06,960
It's a perfect balance.

551
00:27:07,260 --> 00:27:08,380
No competition.

552
00:27:10,170 --> 00:27:11,100
I'm different.

553
00:27:11,780 --> 00:27:12,780
I have an older brother

554
00:27:13,540 --> 00:27:14,460
and a younger brother.

555
00:27:15,180 --> 00:27:16,300
I'm caught between them.

556
00:27:17,020 --> 00:27:18,820
I barely get a chance to show up.

557
00:27:20,180 --> 00:27:21,340
Things like this

558
00:27:21,340 --> 00:27:22,600
aren't something we can decide.

559
00:27:22,940 --> 00:27:24,100
Just focus on doing your best.

560
00:27:29,580 --> 00:27:30,420
Hey.

561
00:27:30,580 --> 00:27:31,420
Yu.

562
00:27:31,800 --> 00:27:33,380
- Overly friendly.
- What a coincidence.

563
00:27:33,380 --> 00:27:34,220
Here we go again.

564
00:27:35,260 --> 00:27:36,300
Xuan.

565
00:27:36,300 --> 00:27:37,140
You're here too?

566
00:27:37,900 --> 00:27:39,660
I knew you guys would be here.

567
00:27:40,940 --> 00:27:41,780
Bro.

568
00:27:45,940 --> 00:27:47,300
Look at you, so full of yourself.

569
00:27:47,860 --> 00:27:50,220
Who's this girl beside you?

570
00:27:50,220 --> 00:27:51,100
Introduce her.

571
00:27:52,220 --> 00:27:53,060
Xiaoya.

572
00:27:53,220 --> 00:27:54,260
An old classmate.

573
00:27:55,740 --> 00:27:56,580
Hello, everyone.

574
00:27:57,380 --> 00:27:58,220
Hi.

575
00:27:58,860 --> 00:27:59,700
Xuan.

576
00:28:00,100 --> 00:28:00,940
Come on.

577
00:28:01,140 --> 00:28:01,980
Let's continue.

578
00:28:02,980 --> 00:28:04,300
How's your stock trading going?

579
00:28:05,220 --> 00:28:06,660
Don't even mention it.

580
00:28:07,560 --> 00:28:09,300
Just thinking about it
gives me a headache.

581
00:28:09,300 --> 00:28:10,780
What about Mr. Jiang?

582
00:28:10,780 --> 00:28:12,260
Still into stock trading these days?

583
00:28:14,780 --> 00:28:16,340
I heard you've been collecting watches.

584
00:28:17,300 --> 00:28:18,900
