585
00:28:19,420 --> 00:28:20,300
And it got lost.

586
00:28:20,300 --> 00:28:21,620
Ow, my stomach hurts.

587
00:28:21,620 --> 00:28:22,560
I'll step out for a bit.

588
00:28:23,180 --> 00:28:24,920
I heard you switched
from cars to watches.

589
00:28:25,340 --> 00:28:26,460
Stay here.

590
00:28:26,460 --> 00:28:27,640
Which model caught your eye?

591
00:28:34,020 --> 00:28:34,940
Ma'am.

592
00:28:34,940 --> 00:28:36,140
Here's your bill for tonight.

593
00:28:36,140 --> 00:28:37,580
That gentleman earlier didn't pay.

594
00:28:43,300 --> 00:28:45,340
A meal for two costs so much?

595
00:28:47,860 --> 00:28:49,340
I didn't bring enough money.

596
00:28:50,860 --> 00:28:51,940
Zhou's family

597
00:28:53,100 --> 00:28:54,420
went bankrupt ages ago.

598
00:28:54,420 --> 00:28:55,620
Only you

599
00:28:55,620 --> 00:28:56,780
are naively waiting here

600
00:28:56,780 --> 00:28:57,780
and even

601
00:28:57,780 --> 00:28:58,820
paying his bill.

602
00:29:01,140 --> 00:29:02,400
Has he borrowed money from you?

603
00:29:03,220 --> 00:29:04,060
Alright, enough.

604
00:29:05,140 --> 00:29:06,460
Put this bill on my tab.

605
00:29:06,460 --> 00:29:07,400
You can settle it later.

606
00:29:07,860 --> 00:29:08,700
Okay.

607
00:29:15,600 --> 00:29:16,540
Well.

608
00:29:16,730 --> 00:29:17,570
Thanks.

609
00:29:18,140 --> 00:29:18,980
No big deal.

610
00:29:46,620 --> 00:29:48,450
Take a look. Here's an IOU.

611
00:29:52,700 --> 00:29:54,360
I promise I'll pay you back.

612
00:29:54,360 --> 00:29:55,460
But I don't know your name.

613
00:29:55,460 --> 00:29:56,820
So, please fill it in.

614
00:30:06,420 --> 00:30:08,100
So, you're also
into exhibition planning.

615
00:30:08,500 --> 00:30:09,350
Yeah.

616
00:30:09,430 --> 00:30:11,780
The company has a flexible schedule.

617
00:30:11,780 --> 00:30:13,180
When I'm free, I usually like

618
00:30:13,180 --> 00:30:15,100
to play games to pass the time.

619
00:30:16,620 --> 00:30:18,540
My brother's also into gaming.

620
00:30:18,540 --> 00:30:19,540
He even started

621
00:30:19,540 --> 00:30:20,860
some kind of group.

622
00:30:20,860 --> 00:30:21,700
Tianxia Gang.

623
00:30:23,100 --> 00:30:24,020
Tianxia Gang?

624
00:30:25,780 --> 00:30:26,620
Are you

625
00:30:27,060 --> 00:30:28,500
Jiang Anlan's brother?

626
00:30:30,820 --> 00:30:31,820
Do you know Anlan?

627
00:30:33,100 --> 00:30:34,300
I'm a friend of Yao Yuan.

628
00:30:35,060 --> 00:30:36,740
This world is way too small.

629
00:30:37,820 --> 00:30:40,020
We often run into each other
in Shengshi.

630
00:30:40,160 --> 00:30:42,660
I even helped Yao Yuan
marry Jiang Anlan.

631
00:30:42,900 --> 00:30:44,100
She's the master's wife now.

632
00:30:44,580 --> 00:30:45,600
When did they get married?

633
00:30:45,620 --> 00:30:46,980
How come I didn't know about this?

634
00:30:46,980 --> 00:30:47,820
No, that's not it.

635
00:30:47,980 --> 00:30:49,380
It's just a virtual marriage.

636
00:30:49,380 --> 00:30:50,940
It's in the game, not real.

637
00:30:53,580 --> 00:30:54,940
Sorry, I need to take this call.

638
00:30:55,540 --> 00:30:57,820
(Chen)

639
00:30:58,940 --> 00:30:59,780
Ancheng,

640
00:31:00,220 --> 00:31:02,100
your dad seems to want Anlan

641
00:31:02,100 --> 00:31:03,260
to come back to the group.

642
00:31:04,100 --> 00:31:05,620
Looks like you'll have to try harder.

643
00:31:16,900 --> 00:31:19,180
(1967 Music Coffee Bar)

644
00:31:19,180 --> 00:31:20,700
Thank you for coming. Goodbye.

645
00:31:21,140 --> 00:31:22,260
Thanks for today.

646
00:31:22,900 --> 00:31:24,420
Or I wouldn't know what to do.

647
00:31:24,740 --> 00:31:25,660
Don't take it to heart.

648
00:31:26,060 --> 00:31:27,380
But you gotta watch out

649
00:31:27,380 --> 00:31:28,320
for someone like Zhou.

650
00:31:30,260 --> 00:31:31,500
It's his problem,

651
00:31:31,500 --> 00:31:32,340
not yours.

652
00:31:35,190 --> 00:31:36,540
I'll leave now.

653
00:31:36,740 --> 00:31:38,240
I'll call another day to pay you back.

654
00:31:38,740 --> 00:31:39,580
- Goodbye.
- Bye.

655
00:31:50,020 --> 00:31:50,900
Are you drunk?

656
00:31:51,420 --> 00:31:52,900
- No.
- Let me pour you some tea.

657
00:31:55,780 --> 00:31:56,620
Let me.

658
00:32:02,020 --> 00:32:03,340
You had a fight with Anlan?

659
00:32:04,820 --> 00:32:06,380
Ancheng told me about it.

660
00:32:06,620 --> 00:32:08,420
Don't get upset over this.

661
00:32:10,060 --> 00:32:12,220
Anlan needs to think it through.

662
00:32:12,220 --> 00:32:13,900
He's made things so tense.

663
00:32:14,460 --> 00:32:16,220
What if he has to go back
to Jiulong later?

664
00:32:17,750 --> 00:32:18,940
He's still angry.

665
00:32:18,940 --> 00:32:19,980
Don't even bring it up.

666
00:32:22,620 --> 00:32:23,740
Am I angry?

667
00:32:28,420 --> 00:32:29,460
I'm just waiting to see

668
00:32:29,460 --> 00:32:30,860
how he treats that girl next.

669
00:32:31,780 --> 00:32:33,260
That'll show whether he's still doing

670
00:32:33,260 --> 00:32:34,400
whatever he wants.

671
00:32:37,380 --> 00:32:38,340
Alright.

672
00:32:38,340 --> 00:32:39,420
It's getting late.

673
00:32:39,420 --> 00:32:40,700
You should get some rest early.

674
00:32:46,710 --> 00:32:47,780
Look.

675
00:32:48,020 --> 00:32:49,260
He hasn't married her,

676
00:32:49,260 --> 00:32:50,420
and it's already like this.

677
00:32:50,500 --> 00:32:51,930
What's going to happen in the future?

678
00:32:53,810 --> 00:32:54,780
Mrs. Jiang,

679
00:32:54,780 --> 00:32:56,580
I don't know what you're thinking,

680
00:32:57,060 --> 00:32:59,660
but I don't welcome her into our family.

681
00:33:04,860 --> 00:33:05,900
Mrs. Jiang,

682
00:33:05,900 --> 00:33:06,740
don't worry.

683
00:33:07,020 --> 00:33:07,980
I have a plan.

684
00:33:10,980 --> 00:33:11,820
Wenqian,

685
00:33:12,940 --> 00:33:15,020
don't come up with any bad ideas.

686
00:33:16,060 --> 00:33:17,900
Mrs. Jiang, rest assured.

687
00:33:31,300 --> 00:33:32,860
You bought so much.

688
00:33:35,940 --> 00:33:37,300
What exactly did you get?

689
00:33:37,300 --> 00:33:38,500
You'll see when you look.

690
00:33:44,380 --> 00:33:46,340
Management Stories and Philosophy.

691
00:33:47,660 --> 00:33:49,140
Business Secret.

692
00:33:49,460 --> 00:33:51,600
When did you start getting interested
in these books?

693
00:33:53,460 --> 00:33:54,780
After I got involved

694
00:33:54,780 --> 00:33:56,420
with Anlan's family,

695
00:33:56,420 --> 00:33:57,460
I realized something.

696
00:33:57,460 --> 00:33:58,580
If I want to be with him,

697
00:33:59,020 --> 00:34:00,980
I have to work harder.

698
00:34:00,980 --> 00:34:02,580
Only then can you deserve Anlan?

699
00:34:03,500 --> 00:34:06,060
Love isn't about that.

700
00:34:07,140 --> 00:34:08,180
I used to think that too.

701
00:34:08,180 --> 00:34:09,860
No need to compare in a relationship.

702
00:34:10,260 --> 00:34:11,880
To be together, the most important thing

703
00:34:11,880 --> 00:34:12,660
is love.

704
00:34:12,660 --> 00:34:13,500
Right?

705
00:34:14,100 --> 00:34:15,300
But when I'm in a relationship,

706
00:34:16,060 --> 00:34:17,940
I think effort really matters.

707
00:34:18,500 --> 00:34:19,340
Besides,

708
00:34:20,020 --> 00:34:22,260
Anlan is so outstanding.

709
00:34:23,500 --> 00:34:24,340
Yuan,

710
00:34:24,340 --> 00:34:25,860
I know Anlan is amazing,

711
00:34:25,860 --> 00:34:27,620
but you're more impressive.

712
00:34:27,620 --> 00:34:28,660
You're not only beautiful

713
00:34:28,660 --> 00:34:29,740
but also smart.

714
00:34:29,980 --> 00:34:32,140
Their family is truly lucky

715
00:34:32,140 --> 00:34:33,700
to have a daughter-in-law like you.

716
00:34:35,180 --> 00:34:37,140
You can become even better,

717
00:34:37,140 --> 00:34:38,060
but

718
00:34:38,060 --> 00:34:39,340
don't underestimate yourself.

719
00:34:39,340 --> 00:34:41,060
Xinran, I'm not underestimating myself.

720
00:34:41,700 --> 00:34:42,660
I really feel like

721
00:34:43,140 --> 00:34:44,220
Mr. and Mrs. Jiang

722
00:34:44,660 --> 00:34:46,900
have pointed out something
I hadn't considered before.

723
00:34:47,340 --> 00:34:48,720
I think what they said makes sense.

724
00:34:49,660 --> 00:34:51,460
And when I see Anlan at the company,

725
00:34:51,900 --> 00:34:52,980
he's truly outstanding.

726
00:34:53,540 --> 00:34:54,820
I want to work harder, really.

727
00:34:56,100 --> 00:34:57,220
You've grown up.

728
00:34:58,140 --> 00:35:00,140
But if anyone ever treats you badly,

729
00:35:00,140 --> 00:35:00,980
you must tell me.

730
00:35:01,340 --> 00:35:02,180
Okay.

731
00:35:59,620 --> 00:36:00,460
Yuan.

732
00:36:00,810 --> 00:36:01,650
Hey.

733
00:36:01,650 --> 00:36:02,580
Where are you?

734
00:36:02,580 --> 00:36:03,620
I'm right here.

735
00:36:03,620 --> 00:36:05,260
Yuan, you're going to university soon.

736
00:36:05,260 --> 00:36:07,300
We have a gift for you.

737
00:36:07,540 --> 00:36:08,420
A gift?

738
00:36:08,420 --> 00:36:09,340
What is it?

739
00:36:09,340 --> 00:36:10,680
You'll see once you check it out.

740
00:36:11,100 --> 00:36:12,100
What gift is it?

741
00:36:12,100 --> 00:36:13,300
You'll find out very soon.

742
00:36:21,580 --> 00:36:22,740
It's so pretty.

743
00:36:22,740 --> 00:36:23,580
Right?

744
00:36:24,540 --> 00:36:26,800
This is a gift from us
for you getting into university.

745
00:36:27,260 --> 00:36:29,220
We originally wanted to get you a car,

746
00:36:29,700 --> 00:36:32,380
but you know how things are at home now.

747
00:36:32,380 --> 00:36:34,300
So, here's a bicycle for you.

748
00:36:34,300 --> 00:36:35,700
- Do you like it?
- Yeah.

749
00:36:36,060 --> 00:36:37,980
Perfect. Riding's healthy.

750
00:36:37,980 --> 00:36:38,980
I can lose some weight.

751
00:36:38,980 --> 00:36:40,260
I like it. Thanks, Mom, Dad.

752
00:36:42,660 --> 00:36:44,020
After you start university,

753
00:36:44,020 --> 00:36:45,900
a lot of guys will want
to chase after you.

754
00:36:45,900 --> 00:36:47,020
But don't rush

755
00:36:47,020 --> 00:36:48,460
to earn the dating credit.

756
00:36:49,540 --> 00:36:51,380
You're worrying way too early.

757
00:36:51,980 --> 00:36:53,060
No, you don't get it.

758
00:36:53,420 --> 00:36:54,940
These days, once young people

759
00:36:54,940 --> 00:36:57,140
get into university, especially guys,

760
00:36:57,140 --> 00:36:58,500
they're in a hurry to start dating.

761
00:36:58,780 --> 00:36:59,620
Look.

762
00:36:59,620 --> 00:37:00,860
My daughter is so outstanding.

763
00:37:01,580 --> 00:37:03,340
Surely, many guys will be after her.

764
00:37:03,620 --> 00:37:05,180
If you like someone,

765
00:37:05,180 --> 00:37:07,220
you must bring them home to meet us.

766
00:37:07,220 --> 00:37:08,940
- Enough.
- Only if I approve

767
00:37:08,940 --> 00:37:10,020
can things move forward.

768
00:37:11,300 --> 00:37:12,340
Okay, okay.

769
00:37:12,340 --> 00:37:13,740
You gave her a bicycle

770
00:37:13,740 --> 00:37:15,340
with a whole speech attached.

771
00:37:15,900 --> 00:37:17,060
Dad, I get it.

772
00:37:17,060 --> 00:37:18,260
I'll be busy with my studies.

773
00:37:18,260 --> 00:37:20,020
I have to work and study.

774
00:37:20,020 --> 00:37:21,300
I won't have time for dating.

775
00:37:21,300 --> 00:37:22,140
Don't worry.

776
00:37:22,660 --> 00:37:23,500
Ding, ding.

777
00:37:24,300 --> 00:37:25,260
Look here.

778
00:37:25,260 --> 00:37:26,940
You're such a jealous, strict dad.

779
00:37:26,940 --> 00:37:28,540
If Yuan can't find someone,

780
00:37:28,540 --> 00:37:29,420
it'll be your fault.

781
00:37:31,020 --> 00:37:32,820
Our daughter has such great qualities.

782
00:37:32,820 --> 00:37:33,980
She'll surely find someone.

783
00:37:34,340 --> 00:37:36,420
She just needs to be picky.

784
00:37:39,580 --> 00:37:40,580
I'm taking off now.

785
00:37:40,580 --> 00:37:42,020
- Be careful.
- I'm starting now.

786
00:37:42,020 --> 00:37:43,460
- Slow down.
- Watch out.

787
00:38:03,500 --> 00:38:04,500
Dad.

788
00:38:05,820 --> 00:38:06,660
Mom.

789
00:38:09,100 --> 00:38:10,060
Don't worry.

790
00:38:12,380 --> 00:38:13,620
I'll take care of myself.

791
00:38:22,300 --> 00:38:24,020
Is Mrs. Jiang's hand getting better?

792
00:38:24,020 --> 00:38:25,540
Don't. We're not in-laws.

793
00:38:34,100 --> 00:38:35,300
(Check, Shi Zhengyi, 200,000)

794
00:38:37,140 --> 00:38:37,980
What's this?

795
00:38:39,140 --> 00:38:40,300
This money can let you relax

796
00:38:40,300 --> 00:38:42,740
for a while without worries.

797
00:38:43,660 --> 00:38:44,940
Why are you giving me money?

798
00:38:45,500 --> 00:38:47,460
It's to have you persuade
Yao Yuan to back off.

799
00:38:48,060 --> 00:38:48,900
What?

800
00:38:50,460 --> 00:38:51,660
I won't do that.

801
00:38:52,820 --> 00:38:54,160
I'm the one who burned Mrs. Jiang.

802
00:38:54,220 --> 00:38:55,460
Yuan has nothing to do with it.

803
00:38:55,460 --> 00:38:56,500
Don't drag her into this.

804
00:38:57,260 --> 00:38:58,180
Please

805
00:38:58,500 --> 00:38:59,340
take this money back.

806
00:39:02,940 --> 00:39:04,180
From the burn incident alone,

807
00:39:04,180 --> 00:39:05,980
you can see the gap
between our two families.

808
00:39:06,940 --> 00:39:08,860
Our family is wealthy.

809
00:39:09,460 --> 00:39:10,420
Plus,

810
00:39:10,420 --> 00:39:11,860
Anlan is both subjectively

811
00:39:11,860 --> 00:39:13,260
and objectively outstanding.

812
00:39:15,220 --> 00:39:16,980
Yuan's qualities aren't bad either.

813
00:39:17,460 --> 00:39:18,860
Anlan is so outstanding.

814
00:39:19,020 --> 00:39:20,580
The girl he likes must be good.

815
00:39:20,980 --> 00:39:23,460
But there's still a gap between them.

816
00:39:24,540 --> 00:39:26,180
Will their values be the same?

817
00:39:26,500 --> 00:39:28,140
Values aren't something we can decide.

818
00:39:28,780 --> 00:39:30,220
As long as they get along well,

819
00:39:30,220 --> 00:39:31,460
that's what truly matters.

820
00:39:33,940 --> 00:39:35,380
I'm really wasting my breath here.

821
00:39:37,660 --> 00:39:38,620
Listen,

822
00:39:39,140 --> 00:39:41,660
based on my concerns as Anlan's elder,

823
00:39:41,660 --> 00:39:43,740
I won't let Yao Yuan marry him.

824
00:39:45,300 --> 00:39:46,820
Then I have nothing more to say.

825
00:39:47,820 --> 00:39:49,080
I'll pay for the coffee myself.

826
00:39:52,100 --> 00:39:52,940
Stop right there.

827
00:39:54,740 --> 00:39:56,740
Don't tell me you think
the money's too little.

828
00:39:57,920 --> 00:39:59,080
How much exactly would it take

829
00:39:59,080 --> 00:40:00,220
for you to stop Yao Yuan?

830
00:40:06,760 --> 00:40:07,820
Do you think spending money

831
00:40:07,820 --> 00:40:09,500
can buy our feelings?

832
00:40:10,140 --> 00:40:10,980
I'm telling you.

833
00:40:11,780 --> 00:40:12,620
It's impossible.

834
00:40:13,620 --> 00:40:14,980
Yuan has been through so much.

835
00:40:15,540 --> 00:40:17,060
She finally found a good match.

836
00:40:17,060 --> 00:40:18,620
I should be the one giving my blessings.

837
00:40:18,900 --> 00:40:20,040
How could I ever ruin that?

838
00:40:21,060 --> 00:40:22,600
No amount of money could make me do it.

839
00:40:23,380 --> 00:40:24,220
Besides,

840
00:40:24,580 --> 00:40:26,220
their relationship
is between them alone.

841
00:40:26,420 --> 00:40:27,780
I advise you not to get involved.

842
00:40:34,500 --> 00:40:36,220
I'm only trying
to look out for Yao Yuan.

843
00:40:37,220 --> 00:40:38,160
You just don't get it.

844
00:40:43,860 --> 00:40:44,780
What's this?

845
00:40:45,100 --> 00:40:46,540
All the money I have in my account.

846
00:40:47,540 --> 00:40:48,540
Even the IOU is in there.

847
00:40:53,820 --> 00:40:55,120
Thanks for lending me the money,

848
00:40:55,900 --> 00:40:57,460
but I don't want things to come up short

849
00:40:57,740 --> 00:40:59,300
in front of your family

850
00:40:59,900 --> 00:41:00,770
or affect

851
00:41:00,780 --> 00:41:02,060
Yuan's place in your heart.

852
00:41:03,500 --> 00:41:04,570
Why do you say that?

853
00:41:05,010 --> 00:41:07,060
I won't let Yao Yuan suffer
any unfair treatment.

854
00:41:08,700 --> 00:41:10,180
Your aunt came to me with money,

855
00:41:11,020 --> 00:41:12,620
asking me to convince Yuan to leave you.

856
00:41:14,300 --> 00:41:15,740
I didn't know about this,

857
00:41:16,660 --> 00:41:18,020
